# ▶️ Getting Started

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repository.git
cd your-repository
```

---

## Run Week 4 React Application

```bash
cd week4/day20/app
npm install
npm run dev
```

---

## Production Build

```bash
npm run build
npm run preview
```

---

## Run Python Backend

```bash
python -m venv .venv

# Windows
.venv\Scripts\activate

# Linux / macOS
source .venv/bin/activate

pip install -r requirements.txt

python main.py
```

